Since 1979, Lightlife has been committed to creating vegetarian food that is good for you and the planet. We are also committed to promoting a good life for all. That is why Lightlife contributes 5% of its profits to organizations that work to protect children, the environment, and human rights. We believe that together, we can make a difference. Veggie goodness for you and the planet. The tasty and nutritious way to add the savory taste and texture of juicy seasoned ground beef to anything from tacos to burritos to enchiladas! At Lightlife, our passion is delicious food. And because veggie food takes less from the land, each meal is your own, simple way of doing the world, and yourself, a little extra good. Contains 9 grams of protein per serving. 2 cups meatless Smart Ground = 1 lb. browned, drained ground beef. Certified vegan. No nitrites.
